and heres the unmute command

[code] if (command.startsWith(“unmute”) && (playerRights >= 1)) {
try {
String unmuted = command.substring(7);
int unmute = PlayerHandler.getPlayerID(unmutes);
client p = (client) server.playerHandler.players[unmute];

	if (unmute != 0) {
		sM("You successfully un-muted "+unmuted+".");
		p.Muted = false;

		p.sM(""+playerName+" has un-muted you.");
	} else {
		sM("The player you have tried to un-mute isn't online, or doesn't excist.");
	    }

		sM("Try entering the name you want to un-mute.");
	}
}[/code]
